{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9226d952c0","title":"在中华全国文学艺术工作者代表大会上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"006310c792","index":0,"year":1949,"month":7,"day":6,"articleId":"9226d952c0"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d6b2632630","type":"title","text":"在中华全国文学艺术工作者代表大会上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9226d952c0"},{"id":"065b71e7b6","type":"paragraph","text":"同志们，今天我来欢迎你们。你们开的这样的大会是很好的大会，是革命需要的大会，是全国人民所希望的大会。因为你们都是人民所需要的人，你们是人民的文学家、人民的艺术家或者是人民的文学艺术工作的组织者。你们对于革命有好处，对于人民有好处。因为人民需要你们，我们就有理由欢迎你们。再讲一声，我们欢迎你们。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9226d952c0"},{"id":"4543e15ac4","type":"paragraph","text":"1949年7月6日，毛泽东等在中华全国文学艺术工作者代表大会主席台上","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9226d952c0"}],"page":{"id":"bc5e51f86a","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9226d952c0","start":34,"end":34}}}},"__N_SSG":true}